   NAME
	TCC - Closes the tracing console window.

   FORMAT
	TCC

   TEMPLATE
	(none)

   PATH
	REXXC/TCC

   FUNCTION
	TCC closes the global tracing console as soon as all active 
	programs are no longer using it. All read requests queued to the 
	console must be satisfied before it can be closed.

   SEE ALSO
	TCO, TS, TE
